Former Joburg mayor Mpho Moerane's memorial service is being held in Alexandra. * Editor's note: This livestream has ended. You may watch a recording above. JOHANNESBURG - Tributes and messages of condolence have been pouring in for former Joburg mayor Mpho Moerane following news of his passing. Moerane died at Milpark Hospital on Wednesday after sustaining injuries in a car crash last week. READ: Moerane funeral to be held on Sunday A laying of wreaths at the accident site is taking place today followed by a memorial service in Alexandra. Moerane's funeral will be held on Sunday.